   <ext_description linkend="Person_organization_arm.Organization_relationship.related_organization">
 the other instance of <express_ref linkend="person_organization:arm:Person_organization_arm.Organization"/>

 that is part of the relationship. If one element of the relationship is dependent upon the other, this attribute shall be the dependent one.
	 </ext_description>
